HEADWORD: Leptodactylidae
<hw>Leptodactylidae</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>leptodactyl</er>.]</ety> <def>A natural family of New World frogs;
in some classifications it is essentially coextensive with the family
<fam>Bufonidae</fam>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> family <fam>Leptodactylidae</fam>.</syn>⟦br⟧
